title: #92Noon! Cousins/Rudolph/Diggs/Spielman/Birk
description: PA is LIVE from the Twin Cities Orthopedics Performance Center as the Vikings prepare for the 2018 NFL Draft! New Vikings QB Kirk Cousins stops by the nice new studio. Kyle Rudolph and Stefon Diggs share how life has been post-Minneapolis Miracle. After Mike Zimmer stops in for a brief interview, Rick Spielman previews the Draft. And Birk Bit closes out the show!
